Pavel Machek wrote:
> Oh, well, you'll have to type open("/overlay/#url:type:||some|uri")
> for reasons described on the page.
I'd be inclined to put
   type://server/location -> /url/type://server/location
   type:/location         -> /url/type://localhost/location
translation in the shell, just like ~ expansion.
Stick with POSIX *and* look good :-)
